            <tr>
                <td>STEP 2:   </td>
                <td>
                    Fill out the <a href="ContactUs.html">CONTACT US</a> form on website. This holds your date on our calendar until your deposit is 	 	   received.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>STEP 3:   </td>
