                    held on our calendar, please be <b>mindful</b> to release that date by notifying our office.  If we receive a
                    request that conflicts with your date prior to receiving your deposit, you will get first right of refusal.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>STEP 4:   </td>
                <td>Upon receiving confirmation, please review <b>ALL DETAILS</b> and verify correctness of the date, serving 	 	   time, serving address, and cell number for day of event. </td>
