            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>STEP 6:   </td>
                <td>Three days prior to the event, you will receive a call from your Flipper</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>STEP 7:   </td>
                <td>Chris Cakes is user friendly -- we do all the hard work. Organize 2-3 volunteers, sell your tickets, and 	  	   together this ensures you’ll have a fun and profitable experience. </td>
